moduleMetadataJson.name: Canon IR-Adv Password Extractor
moduleMetadataJson.description:
This module will extract the passwords from address books on various Canon IR-Adv mfp devices.
        Tested models:
        iR-ADV C2030,
        iR-ADV 4045,
        iR-ADV C5030,
        iR-ADV C5235,
        iR-ADV C5240,
        iR-ADV 6055,
        iR-ADV C7065
